snippet.textDisplay: Look at Atif's body language, he is truly living the lyrics of the song. Pay attention to the richness of  emotion (Bhava) he brings to the song.  Both negative situations - loneliness, desperation, poverty, suffering etc. as well as positive emotions - love, reverence, gratitude, surrender, inspiration etc. are beautifully expressed by Atif. Every syllable is given true justice. Not to mention his technical perfection and quality of voice.  I refuse to believe that this level of excellence is just the result of training. No, this is a gift, divinity is being expressed through a medium who we know as our beloved Atif Aslam. How blessed we are to be able to listen to this song at a moments notice on Youtube.
